ne groups receivables under their Invoice tag.\ntest bal assets:receiv --pivot Invoice\n           38.00 GBP  Invoice\n           11.00 GBP    102:Assets:Receivables\n           12.00 GBP    103:Assets:Receivables\n           15.00 GBP    104:Assets:Receivables\n--------------------\n           38.00 GBP\nend test\n\n; --group-by combined with --pivot must show every group that has a\n; matching posting, with the pivoted account hierarchy underneath each\n; group's title.  Before the fix, BBB's group was silently dropped.\ntest bal assets:receiv --group-by \"tag('Customer')\" --pivot Invoice\nAAA\n           27.00 GBP  Invoice\n           12.00 GBP    103:Assets:Receivables\n           15.00 GBP    104:Assets:Receivables\n--------------------\n           27.00 GBP\n\nBBB\n           11.00 GBP  Invoice:102:Assets:Receivables\nend test\n\n; The same combination must work for register reports as well.\ntest reg assets:receiv --group-by \"tag('Customer')\" --pivot Invoice\nAAA\n2011/02/01 Sell to customer AAA In:10:Asse:Receivables    10.00 GBP    10.00 GBP\n2011/02/03 Sell to customer AAA In:10:Asse:Receivables    12.00 GBP    22.00 GBP\n2011/02/04 Sell to customer AAA In:10:Asse:Receivables    15.00 GBP    37.00 GBP\n2011/02/03 Money received fro.. In:10:Asse:Receivables   -10.00 GBP    27.00 GBP\n\nBBB\n2011/02/02 Sell to customer BBB In:10:Asse:Receivables    11.00 GBP    11.00 GBP\nend test\n",
